{"id":171930,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011812/","date":"2011-08-13T01:00:23Z","modified":"2011-08-13T01:00:23Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/8/12","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904823804576501990544200426.html?mod=googlenews_wsj\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾未未继续挑战北京</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他发推，呛声，让当局进退两</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">难</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/12/us-china-unrest-idUSTRE77B07S20110812\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周四，贵州黔西发生骚乱</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，居民走上街头，推翻警车，抗议城管粗暴执</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/12/world/asia/12train.html?_r=1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上月动车事故后，中国停止审批新铁路项目</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，但是在建项目仍在进行，只是要重新检查安</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">全</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《长城内外》博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/08/11/7347941-relations-between-uighurs-and-han-chinese-not-all-bad\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新疆的维汉关系并不一团漆黑</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>MSNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">采访了一位有趣的维族青</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/12/world/asia/12lama.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国认定的班禅喇嘛访问拉卜楞寺</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，外国游客被劝离夏</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">河</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/11/are-china%E2%80%99s-national-treasures-safe-inside-the-forbidden-city/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">故宫国宝安全成</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">疑</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲时报在线</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.atimes.com/atimes/China/MH13Ad01.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">王光亚最近访港并频频发表公开讲话</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，本文认为作为主权国家的代表，王为北京说话是正常的，何况他的话还有一些是对的</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">呢</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21525960\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国航母，名字未定，目标不</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">清</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国海军向前迈出一大步但意图还不清楚</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CSIS</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上的访谈：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://csis.org/publication/chinas-aircraft-carrier-threat-us-interests\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的航母对美国利益造成了威胁吗</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？——一艘废弃的老航母改造而成的这艘在军事上不大会造成威胁，</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">但</span></span><span><span>…</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《路透社》：周二数据显示，美中贸易逆差</span></span><span><span>2011</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上半年增长</span></span><span><span>12%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/11/us-china-usa-trade-idUSTRE77A5N220110811\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国会可能会在汇率问题上更强</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">硬</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《旧金山纪事报》：美国报告失业率降低，以及猜测中国政府不会加息，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/g/a/2011/08/11/bloomberg1376-LPSIBD6JTSE801-71SKKPI24FR39B9SB83JAKVG33.DTL\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国股市连续第三天上</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">涨</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/stephen-harper-plans-china-trip-to-strengthen-ties/article2126005/?utm_medium=Feeds:%20RSS/Atom\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">哈珀总理计划</span>11<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月访华，为加中政治经贸关系定下新的基调</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>7</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月份加拿大遣返赖昌星有助于双方关</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">系</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：【排行榜】福山核电站事故不过是最近一次政府忙于掩盖错误，同时有人丧命的例子而已，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/09/nothing_to_see_here?page=full\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">这儿还有更多</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。呃，中国又上榜了，两次</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/crime/8697018/London-riots-live.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">伦敦和英国骚乱</span>8<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span>11<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：大批抢劫者被推上法庭，议员回应卡梅隆对国会的讲</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">话</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/10/the_kids_aren_t_alright\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年轻人有问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——伦敦及其他城市的骚乱并非明显政治抗议，但也不仅是大规模犯罪活</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">动</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2011/aug/11/malaysian-ashraf-haziq-riots\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在伦敦骚乱中被打劫的马来西亚人仍人英国仍然是个伟大的地</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">方</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：周四，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/08/11/afghanistan.chopper.us.killed/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国防部公布了在阿富汗直升机袭击中丧生的美国军人名单</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>30</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名美国人丧生，其中</span></span><span><span>17</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人为海豹突击队</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">员</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/08/11/afghanistan.troops.killed/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">再有</span>5<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名美国士兵在阿富汗南部遭袭击身</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亡</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/09/three_cheers_for_decline\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为美国衰落三呼万岁</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——降低美国的全球野心也许能让美国成为一个更加健康更加快乐的国</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">家</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/meast/08/11/israel.new.housing/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fcnn_world+%28RSS%3A+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以色列批准在东耶路撒冷新建</span>2700<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">幢住</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">宅</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CEIP</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=45322&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+CarnegieEndowmentForInternationalPeaceGeneralPublicationsAndEvents+(DC+-+General+Publications+and+Events)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">埃及和突尼斯的过渡政府都面临危险</span></a> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——两地的选举都推迟了，而过渡政府是迅速组建起来进行选举的临时政府，他们的合法性在流</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">失</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/10/cairos_revolutionaries_change_tactics?page=full\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">开罗的革命者们在调整策略</span></a> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他们在寻找新的途径制造影响，选举看来前途不妙，他们是否在失守阵地</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21525847\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国国际基金：这个辛迪加在非洲主宰着中国的石油贸易</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，这是个中国政府控制的基金</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">吗</span>？</span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/china-regulators-said-to-tell-banks-to-tighten-curbs-on-property-lending.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国监管者告诉银行收紧房贷</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。预期未来数月内政府继续其打压房价措</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">施</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲时报在线</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.atimes.com/atimes/China_Business/MH13Cb01.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">随着全球经济在美欧债务危机的阴影下增长放缓，中国的出口前景不</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">妙</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21525968\">10<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年沉寂之后，马来西亚槟城经济再度繁荣</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。槟城拥有低成本和高科技双重优势</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CFR</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">访谈：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.cfr.org/cybersecurity/cybertheft-us-economy/p25639?cid=rss-fullfeed-cybertheft_and_the_u.s._econom-081111&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+cfr_main+(CFR.org+-+Main+Site+Feed)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">网络盗窃与美国的经济</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">迈克菲的安全专家谈知识产权通过网络被窃取会让美国的经济衰退、失业增加、竞争力下</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">降</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透分析：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/12/us-usa-manufacturing-china-idUSTRE77B2IV20110812\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的成本开始让美国跨国公司担心了</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——路透分析一般来说比消息要深入，比深度调查要浅显，喜欢这口的同学可以</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">译</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/12/soft-power-smackdown-confucius-institute-vs-taiwan-academy/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">软实力对决！孔子学院</span> vs. <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾学院</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21525966\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">福岛核危机</span>5<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月后，还有</span>1<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万多人居住在临时庇护所</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。政府无所作为，人民自发设立网站，监控和收集核辐射状</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">况</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：译者Podcast已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；需翻墙更新下载。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-824825504172725252?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":947,"categories":[1],"tags":[10091]}